  <brief_title>The Effectiveness of Dual Therapy (Lopinavir/Ritonavir + LamivudinE) in Treatment-Experienced HIV Infected Patients in the Russian Federation</brief_title>
  <acronym>SIMPLE</acronym>
  <official_title>ProSpective, MultI-Center, Observational PrograM to Assess the Effectiveness of Dual TheraPy (Lopinavir/Ritonavir + LamivudinE) in Treatment-Experienced HIV Infected Patients in the Routine Clinical Settings of the Russian Federation</official_title>
